Item 2.  Properties
 
We lease office space facilities for our corporate headquarters in Norwalk, Connecticut, United States of America. We
lease additional space, including office space and data center facilities in various locations around the world, to support our
operations, the largest being the headquarters of our Booking.com business in Amsterdam, Netherlands. Other than the office
building for the future headquarters of the Booking.com brand that is currently under construction in the Netherlands and the
associated land-use rights (see the section "Land-use rights" within Note 2 to our Consolidated Financial Statements for more
details, which is incorporated into this Item 2 by reference thereto), we did not own any real estate at December 31, 2018.
 
We believe that our existing facilities are adequate to meet our current requirements, and that suitable additional or
substitute space will be available as needed to accommodate any further expansion of corporate operations.
 
