In March 2015, the Company issued Senior Notes due March 3, 2027, with an interest rate of 1.8% (the "2027 Notes") for
an aggregate principal amount of 1.0 billion Euros. The 2027 Notes were issued with an initial discount of 0.3 million Euros. In
addition, the Company paid $6 million in debt issuance costs during the year ended December 31, 2015. Interest on the 2027 Notes
